description:
Before he was assassinated, John Kennedy said he was going to “splinter the CIA into a thousand pieces and scatter it to the wind.” The CIA acts in  many corrupt, unconstitutional ways, and JFK was at odds with the CIA. Maybe this is why he was assassinated?
